OL,3,CCalls for compensation for mothers of
OL,4,Cchildren affected after taking
OL,5,Cvalproate
OL,7,FIt's been described as "a bigger
OL,8,Fhealth scandal than thalidomide". How
OL,9,Fthousands of babies in the UK were
OL,10,Fborn with disabilities, after their
OL,11,Fmothers weren't warned of the dangers
OL,12,Fof taking the epilepsy drug valproate
OL,13,Fduring pregnancy.
OL,15,FA report out today calls for the
OL,16,Ffamilies to get urgent financial help
OL,17,Ffrom the government.
OL,19,FA mother from Keyworth in
OL,20,FNottinghamshire was among those at the
OL,21,Flaunch in Westminster.
