OL,7,FCatherine Cox's son Matthew, who is
OL,8,F22, has learning difficulties and is
OL,9,Fon the auitisiic spectrum.
OL,11,FCatherine was taking valproate when
OL,12,Fshe was pregnant, she said doctors
OL,13,Fnever told her it could harm her baby
OL,14,F- but that's not stopped her feeling
OL,15,Fguilty.
OL,17,FVALPROATE TIMELINE:
OL,19,FSodium valproate was first licensed in
OL,20,Fthe UK in 1973. Tests on animals had
OL,21,Fshown it could harm foetuses.
