OL,7,FBut the body responsible for
OL,8,Fregulating medicines thought it best
OL,9,Fnot to alert patients, saying "it
OL,10,Fcould give rise to fruitless anxiety".
OL,12,FIn the 1980s, academics began raising
OL,13,Fconcerns about possible harm to unborn
OL,14,Fbabies.
OL,16,FA group of families brought a court
OL,17,Fcase against the drug manufacturer,
OL,18,Fbut in 2010 it was dropped after legal
OL,19,Faid was withdrawn.
