OL,7,FIn 2020, a report by Baroness
OL,8,FCumberlege said more than 20 thousand
OL,9,Fbabies had been affected. She called
OL,10,Ffor compensation for the families. So
OL,11,Ffar they haven't received a penny.
OL,13,FCathrine says Matthew will never be
OL,14,Fable to live independently and that
OL,15,Fit's time for the government to do
OL,16,Fwhat's right by him.
