OL,7,FThe report has outlined many
OL,8,Fsuggestions, the patient safety
OL,9,Fcommissioner has called for an
OL,10,Fimmediate compensation of #100,000 for
OL,11,Fthose who were harmed.
OL,13,FIn response, women's health minister,
OL,14,FMaria Caulfield, said: "Our sympathies
OL,15,Fremain with those affected by sodium
OL,16,Fvalproate and pelvic mesh and we are
OL,17,Ffocused on improving how the system
OL,18,Flistens to patients and healthcare
OL,19,Fprofessionals, as well as introducing
OL,20,Fmeasures to make medicines and devices
OL,21,Fsafer.
